ebsEnabled.description: Whether EBS volumes are attached to data nodes in the domain.

iops.description: Baseline input/output (I/O) performance of EBS volumes attached to data nodes. Applicable only for the GP3 and Provisioned IOPS EBS volume types.

throughput.description: Specifies the throughput (in MiB/s) of the EBS volumes attached to data nodes. Applicable only for the gp3 volume type.

volumeSize.description: Size of EBS volumes attached to data nodes (in GiB).

volumeType.description: Type of EBS volumes attached to data nodes.
